data.description: It's rare to see a customized, charming, cabin-like home like this one. This comfortable home has unbelievable personalized craftsmanship with a vintage touch. Now it's time for you to use your own 21st Century style to make this home your own. Homes like this one rarely come on the market where there has been so much love and attention to detail. Make this your home sweet home in Fremont. Enjoy being minutes away from Lake Elizabeth for a family picnic or frolic. It's also conveniently located close to shopping and delicious eateries. For commuters, take advantage of easy access to freeways. Schedule a showing with your realtor or with me!
